Bluetongue, Germany
-------------------
Information received on (and dated) 6 Nov 2008 from Mr Werner Zwingmann,
Ministerialdirigent, "Leiter der Unterabteilung Tiergesundheit und
Lebensmittelhygiene," Bundesministerium fur Ernahrung, Landwirtschaft und
Verbraucherschutz (BMELV), Bonn, Germany

Summary
Report type: immediate notification
Start date: 3 Nov 2008
Date of 1st confirmation of the event: 5 Nov 2008
Date submitted to OIE: 6 Nov 2008
Reason for notification: new strain of a listed disease
Causal agent: Bluetongue virus serotype 6
Nature of diagnosis: clinical, laboratory (advanced)
This event pertains to the whole country

New outbreaks:
Outbreak 1 (03456A080058): Halle, Halle, Grafschaft Bentheim, Niedersachsen
